headline: Heartland Mid Cap Value Fund Q2 2025 Commentary
summary: Mid Cap Value Fund lost 0.22% in Q2, trailing the Russell Midcap Value Index, which was up 5.35%. Stock selection was responsible for most of our underperformance.
